OL,6,FThe former deputy leader of the
OL,7,FLiberal Democrats has said he found it
OL,8,F''shocking'' and ''distressing to
OL,9,Frealise'' that he'd been targeted
OL,10,Funlawfully by the publisher of the
OL,11,FDaily Mail and Mail on Sunday ''for
OL,12,Fprofit".
OL,14,FAssociated Newspapers strongly deny
OL,15,FSir Simon Hughes' allegations and
OL,16,Fdescribe his account as ''untruthful
OL,17,Fand convoluted".
