OL,6,FSir Simon is giving evidence as one of
OL,7,Fseven claimants, including Prince
OL,8,FHarry, Sir Elton John and Baroness
OL,9,FDoreen Lawrence, in a high-profile
OL,10,Fprivacy case at the High Court.
OL,12,FHe already won substantial damages
OL,13,Ffrom New Group Newspapers after the
OL,14,FSun printed revelations about his
OL,15,Fsexuality back in 2006.
OL,17,FHe alleges he was also targeted by
OL,18,FAssociated Newspapers, although no
OL,19,Fstories were ever published.
