OL,6,F''The fact that they have remained
OL,7,Fcompletely unapologetic for this
OL,8,Fillegal behaviour is also
OL,9,Fdistressing,'' he said in a statement
OL,10,Fto the court.
OL,12,FBut under cross-examination, Sir Simon
OL,13,Fwas forced to deny he first knew about
OL,14,Fthe case being built against the Mail
OL,15,Fa decade ago.
OL,17,FAntony White KC, barrister for
OL,18,FAssociated Newspapers, suggested that
OL,19,Fhe'd been shown evidence from a so-
OL,20,Fcalled whistleblower at a meeting in
OL,21,F2016.
